nhc_headline: ...PRISCILLA BRINGING HIGH SURF AND GUSTY WINDS TO THE PACIFIC COAST OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR...
summary: ...PRISCILLA BRINGING HIGH SURF AND GUSTY WINDS TO THE PACIFIC COAST OF BAJA CALIFORNIA SUR... As of 8:00 AM MST Wed Oct 08 the center of Priscilla was located near 21.4, -112.5 with movement NW at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 982 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 75 mph.
